waveform.<br>
[0027] FIG. 6 is another schematic representation of a partition of subcarriers in a DAB<br>
waveform.<br>
[0028] FIG. 7 is a schematic representation of reference subcarriers in a lower sideband of<br>
a DAB waveform.<br>
[0029] FIG. 8 is a schematic representation of reference subcarriers in an upper sideband<br>
of a DAB waveform.<br>
[0030] FIG. 9 is a functional block diagram of protocol stack used in a transmitter in a<br>
digital audio broadcasting system.<br>
[0031] FIG. 10 is a functional block diagram of the modem/physical layer of the protocol<br>
stack used in a transmitter in a digital audio broadcasting system.<br>
