n. For notational convenience, the output of OFDM Subcarrier Mapping described above<br>
did not use the subscript n. Rather, it referred to the vector X as representing a single<br>
OFDM symbol. In the following description, the subscript is appended to X because of the<br>
significance of n to OFDM Signal Generation.<br>
